# Per-host, per-model acc-config.yaml overlays.
#
# Tracked by default — committing these makes them available on every
# test host via `git pull` (no out-of-band sync needed).  The original
# design (operator-local only) was overkill for a single-operator
# project where each overlay is already host-scoped (lighthouse-*.yaml).
#
# Add entries below if you ever need to exclude an overlay (e.g. one
# that contains secrets).  Prefer ACC_LLM_API_KEY_ENV pointing at an
# env var over baking the secret into the yaml.

# Local backups created by ../../scripts/sync-host-config.sh
*.bak.*
